text: Parametaria dupontii, the Dupont's dove shell or false cone, is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails.Biolib ==Description== Shells of Parametaria dupontii can reach a length of about .WMSDB – Worldwide Mollusc Species Data Base ==Distribution== This species can be found in Gulf of California and in Pacific Mexico. ==References== Category:Columbellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1845
